	   <tr><td colspan=2>Haste items and spells do stack, but currently bard haste songs do not stack.  VI is aware of that, but no fix is in and is considered a low priority.  Too bad, too.  Just think how nice it would be to add a bard haste song to SLTW and natural item haste.  Couldn't imagine how quick an epic monk would be  =)<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
